{"tid":1056710,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩屌到個阿伯起曬火","createTime":"2019-03-11T11:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T06:33:58.000Z","uid":135689,"like":3,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"72e460f350eb795f7310e0af0e2d7e1089d81c66","tid":1056710,"uid":135689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:25:21.000Z","msg":"我放左啲書係某個位 做緊其他野 <br />\n個阿伯就攞黎睇 我冇為意 跟住佢唔小心整跳曬我啲書 <br />\n我即刻行過去屌鳩佢 <br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。阿伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n：喂啲書我架喎<br />\n：喔 唔好意思 （佢想走）<br />\n咁我見佢走 唔執野 就屌佢講對唔住<br />\n：你講聲對唔住先<br />\n：點解我要講！啲書你放係公家地方，又冇寫你名，整跌咪跌，執番比你囉<br />\n跟住執完又屌住行 我就講唔該 <br />\n佢走完又番翻黎再屌我 最尾我講多聲拜拜<br />\n我諗佢番屋企嬲到食唔到飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c1ae2ae22a5a526a6b67c82781bba1b49d6f78","tid":1056710,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:26:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b09d96c1c9f61f8113c4fc2e833b7700050876e","tid":1056710,"uid":92278,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:28:43.000Z","msg":"樓主好霸氣<br />\n<br />\n含ok?"},{"pid":"2d7c9b30cdd77854bc919e9d3346a35318660a42","tid":1056710,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:30:23.000Z","msg":"屌啲廢老就啱喇"},{"pid":"99f26a4b0da59680fb81d29f2c3310a302b2f589","tid":1056710,"uid":76747,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:32:40.000Z","msg":"無我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。阿伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;既?"},{"pid":"28e275d0fabfd4529d4d9311dc3b17d5c25d4815","tid":1056710,"uid":54791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:37:12.000Z","msg":"首先，啲書冇寫你名邊個都攞得黎睇<br />\n第二，人地一開始已經講左唔好意思，買你怕急急腳走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" clas